quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  43,24,"“Adanena (mneneri wawo): “Ngakhale ndakubweretserani chipembedzo chabwino kuposa chomwe mudawapeza nacho makolo anu (mupitirizabe kutsatira chipembedzo cha makolo anucho)?” Adanena: “Ife tikuzikana zimene mwatumidwa nazozi.”"
  43,25,“Choncho tidawalanga iwo. Taona m’mene adalili mapeto a otsutsa aja
  43,26,"“Ndipo (kumbuka) pamene Ibrahim adauza bambo wake ndi anthu ake (kuti): “Ndithu ine ndadzipatula ku zimene mukuzipembedzazi.”"
  43,27,““Kupatula Amene adandilenga; ndithu Iye andiongola.”
  43,28,"“Ndipo adalichita liwu ili kukhala losatha ku mtundu wake, kuti abwelere (ku malankhulidwe amenewa)"
  43,29,“Koma ndidawasangalatsa awa (Aquraish) pamodzi ndi makolo awo kufikira choonadi chawadzera ndi Mtumiki wolongosola (za choonadichi)
  43,30,"“Ndipo pamene choonadi (Qur’an) chidawadzera, adanena: “Awa ndi matsenga; ndithu ife tikuwakana.”"
  43,31,"“Ndipo adatinso: “Nchifukwa ninji Qur’an iyi siidavumbulutsidwe pa munthu wamkulu mmidzi iwiriyi (Makka ndi Twaif).”"
  43,32,"“(Choncho Allah akunena): “Kodi iwo ndi amene akugawa mtendere wa Mbuye wako (kumpatsa amene wamfuna ndi kummana amene sakumfuna? Chikhalirecho) Ife ndi Amene timagawa pakati pawo zofunika pa moyo wawo mu moyo wadziko lapansi; ndipo tawatukula ena mwa iwo pa ulemelero pamwamba pa ena, choncho ena mwa iwo akuwachita anzawo kukhala antchito awo koma mtendere wa Mbuye wako ndi wabwino kuposa zimene akusonkhanitsa.”"
  43,33,"“Ndipo pakadapanda kuopera kuti anthu adzakhala gulu limodzi (lokanira Allah), ndithu tikadazichita nyumba za amene akumkana (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri kukhala ndi madenga a Siliva, ndi makwelero amene amakwelera (kukhalanso a Siliva)"
  43,34,“Ndipo nyumba zawo kukhala ndi zitseko ndi makama (mabedi) omwe amayadzamira (zonsezo kukhala za Siliva)
  43,35,"“Ndiponso ndi zokongoletsa za golide. Koma zonsezo sikanthu ayi, ndi chisangalalo chabe cha dziko lapansi (chosakhalira kutha); ndipo tsiku lachimaliziro lomwe lili kwa Mbuye wako ndi la oopa Allah (potsatira malamulo Ake ndi kusiya zoletsedwa)"
  43,36,"“Ndipo amene akunyozera kukumbukira (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri, timpatsa satana, kuti iye akhale bwenzi lake (lotsagana nalo)"
  43,37,“Ndipo iwo amawatsekereza ku njira zabwino ndi kumaganiza kuti iwo ngoongoka
  43,38,"“Kufikira pamene adzatidzera (tsiku la Qiyâma, uku akulowetsedwa ku Moto). Adzati (kumuuza satana): “Kalanga ine! Pakati pa ine ndi iwe pakadakhala ntunda wa pakati pa kuvuma ndi kuzambwe (kutalikirana kwathu).” Ha! Taonani kuipa kwa bwenzi"
  43,39,"“(Allah adzawauza kuti): “Ndipo lero sikukuthandizani kukhala limodzi kwanu m’chilango pakuti mudadzichitira nokha zoipa.”"
  43,40,"“Kodi ungathe kuwamveretsa agonthi, kapena ungathe kuwaongola akhungu ndi amene ali mkusokera koonekera"
  43,41,"“Ngati titakuchotsa (padziko usadaone chilango chawo, usakhale ndi chikaiko), ndithu Ife tiwalanga iwo"
  43,42,“Kapena tikusonyeza zimene tidawalonjeza (uona ndi maso ako usadafe). Ndithu Ife tili ndi mphamvu pa iwo
  43,43,"“Choncho, gwiritsa zimene zavumbulutsidwa kwa iwe, ndithu iwe uli pa njira yolunjika"
  43,44,“Ndithu iyi (Qur’an) ndi ulemelero wako ndi anthu ako; ndipo posachedwa mufunsidwa (za ulemelero umenewu)
  43,45,"“Ndipo afunse atumiki Athu amene tidawatumiza iwe usadadze: “Kodi tidapanga milungu ina kuti ipembedzedwe, osati (Allah) Wachifundo chambiri?”"
  43,46,"“Ndithu tidamtumiza Mûsa pamodzi ndi zozizwitsa Zathu kwa Farawo ndi nduna zake; ndipo adati: “Ndithu ine ndine Mtumiki wa Mbuye wa zolengedwa.”"
  43,47,"“Koma pamene adawadzera ndi zisonyezo zathu, basi iwo adali kuziseka"
  43,48,“Ndipo chisonyezo chilichonse chomwe tidawasonyeza chidali chachikulu kuposa chinzake (komabe sadakhulupirire). Ndipo tidawalanga ndi chilango kuti abwelere (kwa Ife)
  43,49,"“Ndipo adati (kwa Mûsa): “E iwe wamatsenga! Tipemphere kwa Mbuye wako pa chomwe adakulonjeza; ndithu ife tiongoka, (tikhulupirira).”"
  43,50,"“Choncho, pamene tidawachotsera chilangocho, basi iwo adayamba kuswa pangano"
  43,51,"“Ndipo Farawo adaitana anthu ake, adati: “E inu anthu anga! Kodi ulamuliro wa mu Iguputo siwanga pamodzi ndi mitsinje iyi imene ikuyenda pansi panga (pa nyumba zanga?) Kodi simukuona?”"
  43,52,"““Kodi kapena ine sindine woposa uyu (Mûsa) wonyozeka, ndipo sangathe kuyankhula momveka?”"
  43,53,““Nanga bwanji sadavekedwe zibangiri zagolide kapena angelo kudza pamodzi ndi iye uku akumtsatira?”
  43,54,“Adawapeputsa anthu ake. Ndipo adamvera; iwo adali anthu otuluka mchilamulo (cha Allah)
  43,55,"“Pamene adatikwiitsa, tidawalanga ndipo tidawamiza onse mmadzi"
  43,56,“Tidawachita (Farawo ndi anthu ake) kukhala chitsanzo cha okanira a pambuyo pawo ndikukhala mbiri kwa anthu amene akudza